{"tid":860510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日上樓發生左件尷尬嘅事","createTime":"2018-10-13T11:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T12:32:44.000Z","uid":212296,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d92714a3148593e497ab56b6b69321b1bb9c38ce","tid":860510,"uid":212296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日星期6明天就放假，諗住上樓叫人 服侍我放鬆下，咁我就上樓撳鐘見到件ok 嘅，準備入房嘅時候，電話突然響起心諗邊條仆街阻人孰倫，咁我就睇下係邊條友打過嚟，原來係老母打嚟，咁我就緊係以最快速度離開依個地方，費事俾老母聽到有女人淫叫，咁我離開時我見到隻雞帶有一些傷心嘅眼神關房門。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得條女應該起到諗緊沒錢就咪上嚟挽啦"},{"pid":"d81bc14713c98189491680afa5140779de1f6f91","tid":860510,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T12:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01da9b24aafe2e29147474bc9cf81213664004e2","tid":860510,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T12:11:38.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"567471c3c482a8a4b57dec9081f20672814f5c98","tid":860510,"uid":13151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"挽你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"b0eb3fc66953ec9b9671688791fb96cd337a20fc","tid":860510,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"一定要聽電話？"}]}